                  <handDesc>
                     <handNote script="naskh" medium="ink">The text is written in naskh. Two hands are involved in this codex. The first hand has copied <locus from="1" to="15">ff.1-15</locus> (21 lines per page), the second has copied <locus from="16" to="104">ff. 16-104</locus> (19 lines per page), and the first hand has copied the rest of it (17 lines per page).</handNote>
